# Day 39 – PDF Splitter & Merger using Claude AI

## Objective

Built a browser-based PDF Splitter & Merger that allows users to split and merge PDF files without uploading them to external servers.

## Features

- PDF Splitter
- PDF Merger
- Drag & Drop File Upload
- Page Preview
- Page Range Selection
- PDF Download
- Responsive UI
- Dark Mode

## Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript

## Key Learnings

- Client-side PDF processing
- File handling using JavaScript
- Interactive UI design
- Drag-and-drop functionality
- Building offline web applications

## Outcome

Successfully developed and tested an offline PDF utility with splitting and merging capabilities.
